{"type":"message","id":"c6ed667e","parentId":"915a542f","timestamp":"2026-03-30T22:29:44.452Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here are some of the skills I can assist you with:\n\n1. **Information Retrieval**:\n   - Search the web for information.\n   - Fetch and extract content from URLs.\n\n2. **Text Processing**:\n   - Convert text to speech.\n   - Extract data from documents or web pages.\n\n3. **Task Automation**:\n   - Automate tasks using browser automation tools.\n   - Control and manage sub-agents for complex workflows.\n\n4. **Memory and Recall**:\n   - Search and retrieve information from memory documents.\n   - Keep track of past conversations and decisions.\n\n5. **Session Management**:\n   - List active sessions and their details.\n   - Send messages to specific sessions.\n   - Spawn new sessions for isolated tasks.\n\n6. **Agent Management**:\n   - List available agents.\n   - Manage sub-agents and their tasks.\n\n7. **Status and Monitoring**:\n   - Check the status of sessions.\n   - Monitor usage, time, and cost of tasks.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_936294\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"mistral-small:24b","usage":{"input":4096,"output":198,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":4294,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774909768077}}
